---
// Sidebar Widget Component
---

<aside class="sidebar-widget">
  <div class="widget-header">
    <h3>Meet the Explorer</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="widget-content">
    <div class="avatar">
      <div class="avatar-placeholder">TE</div>
    </div>
    <p>Welcome! I'm passionate about exploring the depths of personal growth across all pillars of life, rooted in faith. Join me on this journey of continuous learning and stewardship.</p>
    <a href="/#pillars" class="author-link">Start exploring &rarr;</a>
    
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="X (Twitter)">&#120143;</a>
      <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="Instagram">IG</a>
      <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="YouTube">YT</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .sidebar-widget {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .widget-header {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .widget-header h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: white;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .widget-content {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .avatar-placeholder {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .widget-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .author-link {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color var(--transition-speed);
  }

  .author-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .social-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all var(--transition-speed);
  }

  .social-icon:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
